{"tid":2300670,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"耀才中期多賺逾6成 IPO孖展利息收入急增34倍","createTime":"2020-11-25T16:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T02:32:57.000Z","uid":86449,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5f303831c5bc9081361ff1d09224cc4c09d7c4","tid":2300670,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"耀才證券（1428）公佈截至今年9月底止，中期純利按年升63.4%至3.46億元，每股基本盈利為20.39仙，不派中期息。<br />\n<br />\n集團表示，疫情無阻投資需求，反而吸引大批投資者熱衷大抽新股，及帶動新經濟股熱潮，令大市交投活躍，期內收入增長48%至5.83億元。當中，經紀佣金佔3.67億元，升58.2%；孖展融資利息收入有1.14億元，跌24%；首次公開發售（IPO）融資利息收入有9,532.1萬元，按年大增34.4倍。<br />\n<br />\n期間新開立戶口達6.8萬個 ，令客戶戶口總數增加至40.57萬個，按年增長35.%。另外，截至今年9月底止， 管理客戶資產約536億元，按年上升27.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201125/FU3UUUVNS5AIPIDEGN5WERSYFY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201125%2FFU3UUUVNS5AIPIDEGN5WERSYFY%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=167f666b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201125%2FFU3UUUVNS5AIPIDEGN5WERSYFY%2F&h=e9afc110\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201125/FU3UUUVNS5AIPIDEGN5WERSYFY/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家有有無份進貢利息比耀才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1475051b3b083a9f5a682f1a2a616d31ccf24c14","tid":2300670,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"食屎喇，3.4坐撚到依家，係呀，就係果個空心柱體對上好撚長果條線呀，屌你老母，咁好賺幾時升反上去呀"},{"pid":"58c99a847fe04b96ee1c6d679cef9e379750bd85","tid":2300670,"uid":69081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1475051b3b083a9f5a682f1a2a616d31ccf24c14","tid":2300670,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"食屎喇，3.4坐撚到依家，係呀，就係果個空心柱體對上好撚長果條線呀，屌你老母，咁好賺幾時升反上去呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"巴打果時唔止蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a